It is now apparent that the Change Notification Process, in particular Material Changes in Consumption, is more convoluted than what first appeared. To that end I am proposing the following:

1. A standing meeting to be held on Wednesdays at 2.00pm for the next 4 weeks to address the issues and formalize a Process Flow for each occurrence.
2. Draft Process Flow Documents to be prepared in the interim and passed out ASAP to all relevant parties for comment.
3. All comments/issued to be addressed through the Wednesday meeting.

